title: ‘Whose Line Is It Anyway: Bachelor Nation Edition’
description:
Becca and Rachel play a hilarious game of “Whose Line Is It Anyway: Bachelor Nation Edition.” They are joined by some surprise guests (and fan favorites) from their seasons and have to guess who it is by hearing a line or two from the guest’s time on the show. 

Be sure to rate and subscribe so you never miss an episode.
